{
  "stem": "1502.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were taking the 40 Jews because there were SS from all over Europe in that camp, and they wanted to have a sample of Jews, how to torture Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the brought from our camp for the Jews to that SS training camp to teach them how to deal with Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So it was no picnic to stay there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We stayed there until the invasion of June 6.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "June 6, they wanted to shoot us, but somehow, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we were taking back to Mechelen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That camp was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They all went to the front to Normandy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that by itself is a long episode, which could take a long time to tell.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But I won't stay on on this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The next transport went in August.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The-- in the meantime, they've caught my sister, my brother-in-law and my niece, and they were brought to Mechelen also.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And my-- my niece was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They took her out, and she was placed in a children's camp, and she survived the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My brother-in-law and my sister were not on that Palestinian list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My brother-in-law was deported, then he was killed, never came back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My sister was in Auschwitz, but she came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She survived the-- the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The-- the last transport, that was the 27th transport-- the paper from the Palestinian office was not sufficient.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You had to have a paper, a confirming paper, from the International Red Cross, with a number on which list you are, and with-- which number and which number list exactly.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It had to be very detailed if you're really on the list for exchange.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And my friend, Silbershwartz, did not get that communication from the Red Cross in time, he was deported.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
